yle=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;color:#666666;\">Service:</td><td style=\"padding:6px 0;font-size:14px;color:#333333;\">FedEx Priority Overnight</td></tr></table></td></tr></table><table cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"margin:24px auto;\"><tr><td align=\"center\"><a href=\"{{.URL}}\" style=\"display:inline-block;background-color:#4d148c;color:#ffffff;text-decoration:none;padding:14px 32px;border-radius:6px;font-size:16px;font-weight:bold;\">Reschedule Delivery</a></td></tr></table><p style=\"font-size:13px;color:#999999;margin:16px 0 0;text-align:center;\">If no action is taken within 5 business days, the package will be returned.</p></td></tr><tr><td style=\"padding:16px 24px;background-color:#f9f9f9;border-top:1px solid #eeeeee;\"><p style=\"margin:0;font-size:12px;color:#999999;text-align:center;\">FedEx | fedex.com<br/><a href=\"{{.URL}}\" style=\"color:#4d148c;text-decoration:none;\">Manage notifications</a></p></td></tr></table></td></tr></table>{{.Tracker}}</body></html>",
